Package: termstrc
Type: Package
Title: Term Structure and Credit Spread Estimation
Version: 0.3
Date: 2006-12-15
Author: Robert Ferstl, Josef Hayden
Maintainer: Robert Ferstl <robert.ferstl@wu-wien.ac.at> 
Depends: R (>= 2.4.0)
Description: The package includes three widely-used term structure estimation procedures,
             i.e. the parametric Nelson and Siegel, the Svensson approach and the cubic splines approach according to
             J.Huston and McCulloch. Moreover the traditional way of credit spread calculation is implemented. 
License: GPL
